Name: Element Runner
About the game: Across land, water and clouds! Element Runner is a fun, casual platformer where you can explore worlds filled with grass, water, fire, candy and electricity! Featuring over 8 worlds and 60 levels, this game is a relaxing, completionists dream. With different words to collect, tons of unique enemies to dodge and lots of fun to be had, your journey in Element Runner awaits! NOTE: The game is currently only available on Windows but we will have Mac and Linux versions available one day!
